Jean Worms https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Worms 0 Jean Worms (1884–1943) was a French film actor who appeared in a mixture of leading and supporting roles. Worms played Tsar Nicholas II of Russia in the 1938 film Rasputin. Jean_Worms ( 1884 – 1943 ) was a_French_film_actor who appeared in a_mixture of leading_and_supporting_roles .
